# GAP Architecture Rules for {{DomainNamePascal}}

This file documents the architectural rules enforced by ArchUnit tests. Follow these rules when generating or modifying code.

## Layer Dependencies

```
API → Application → Domain
Application → Domain → Infrastructure
Domain → (no dependencies)
Infrastructure → Domain
```

**Rules:**
- API layer may ONLY access Application and Domain
- Application layer may ONLY access Domain and Infrastructure
- Domain layer may NOT access any other layer
- Infrastructure layer may ONLY access Domain

## Package Structure

| Class Type | Package | Example |
|------------|---------|---------|
| Controllers | `..api..` | `io.pexa.gap.{{BoundedContextKebab}}.api.WorkspaceController` |
| Services | `..application..` | `io.pexa.gap.{{BoundedContextKebab}}.application.WorkspaceService` |
| Repositories | `..infrastructure..` | `io.pexa.gap.{{BoundedContextKebab}}.infrastructure.WorkspaceRepository` |
| Entities | `..domain..` | `io.pexa.gap.{{BoundedContextKebab}}.domain.Workspace` |
| Commands | `..application.commands..` | `io.pexa.gap.{{BoundedContextKebab}}.application.commands.CreateWorkspaceCommand` |
| Queries | `..application.queries..` | `io.pexa.gap.{{BoundedContextKebab}}.application.queries.GetWorkspaceQuery` |
| Events | `..domain.events..` | `io.pexa.gap.{{BoundedContextKebab}}.domain.events.WorkspaceCreatedEvent` |

## Naming Conventions

| Class Type | Required Suffix | Package |
|------------|----------------|---------|
| Controllers | `Controller` | `..api..` |
| Services | `Service` | `..application..` |
| Repositories | `Repository` | `..infrastructure..` |
| Commands | `Command` or `Data` | `..commands..` |
| Queries | `Query` or `Data` | `..queries..` |
| Events | `Event` or `Handler` | `..events..` |

## Required Annotations

| Class Type | Required Annotation |
|------------|---------------------|
| Controllers | `@RestController` |
| Services | `@Service` |
| Repositories | `@Repository` |
| Event Handlers | `@Transactional` (on handle methods) |

## Examples

### Correct

```kotlin
// Controller in API package with correct annotation
package io.pexa.gap.{{BoundedContextKebab}}.api
@RestController
class WorkspaceController(private val service: WorkspaceService)

// Service in Application package
package io.pexa.gap.{{BoundedContextKebab}}.application
@Service
class WorkspaceService(private val repository: WorkspaceRepository)

// Repository in Infrastructure package
package io.pexa.gap.{{BoundedContextKebab}}.infrastructure
@Repository
class WorkspaceRepositoryImpl : WorkspaceRepository

// Event handler with @Transactional
package io.pexa.gap.{{BoundedContextKebab}}.events.handlers
class WorkspaceCreatedEventHandler {
    @Transactional
    fun handle(event: WorkspaceCreatedEvent) { ... }
}
```

### Incorrect

```kotlin
// Controller in wrong package
package io.pexa.gap.{{BoundedContextKebab}}.application
@RestController
class WorkspaceController

// Service without annotation
package io.pexa.gap.{{BoundedContextKebab}}.application
class WorkspaceService

// API accessing Infrastructure directly
package io.pexa.gap.{{BoundedContextKebab}}.api
@RestController
class WorkspaceController(
    private val repository: WorkspaceRepository  // Should use service
)

// Event handler without @Transactional
class WorkspaceCreatedEventHandler {
    fun handle(event: WorkspaceCreatedEvent) { ... }  // Missing @Transactional
}
```

## Verification

Run architecture tests to verify compliance:

```bash
./gradlew test --tests "*ArchitectureTest"
```
